00:55:34,400 --> 00:55:36,000
<font color="yellow">Tapi, aku menunggu
selama sepuluh tahun penuh.</font>

506
00:55:36,000 --> 00:55:38,190
<font color="yellow">Siapa suruh kau melakukannya?</font>

507
00:55:43,690 --> 00:55:45,000
<font color="yellow">Matamu indah.</font>

508
00:55:47,400 --> 00:55:49,000
<font color="yellow">Hidungmu juga.</font>

509
00:55:51,000 --> 00:55:52,500
<font color="yellow">Pipimu juga.</font>

510
00:55:57,690 --> 00:55:59,690
<font color="yellow">Bibirku juga, 'kan?</font>

511
00:56:27,500 --> 00:56:28,500
<font color="yellow">Sedang apa kau?</font>

512
00:56:28,500 --> 00:56:30,900
<font color="yellow">Berfoto,
karena hari ini sangat indah.</font>

513
00:56:32,690 --> 00:56:34,590
<font color="yellow">Wow, kau cantik sekali hari ini.</font>

514
00:56:34,590 --> 00:56:35,590
<font color="yellow">Benarkah?</font>

515
00:56:36,000 --> 00:56:37,590
<font color="yellow">Sini, biar aku saja yang
ambil fotonya.</font>

516
00:56:37,590 --> 00:56:39,590
<font color="yellow">Aku?/
Ya!</font>

517
00:56:39,590 --> 00:56:41,300
<font color="yellow">Berdiri di sana.</font>

518
00:56:41,300 --> 00:56:42,590
<font color="yellow">Aku malu.</font>

519
00:56:42,590 --> 00:56:44,590
<font color="yellow">Cepat!</font>

520
00:56:46,000 --> 00:56:51,500
<font color="yellow">Baiklah.
Satu, dua...</font>

521
00:56:51,500 --> 00:56:53,000
<font color="yellow">Tunggu.</font>

522
00:56:53,000 --> 00:56:54,800
<font color="yellow">Apa?</font>

523
00:56:54,800 --> 00:56:58,900
<font color="yellow">Hei. Mana cincinmu?</font>

524
00:56:58,900 --> 00:57:00,000
<font color="yellow">Apa maksudmu?</font>

525
00:57:00,690 --> 00:57:03,800
<font color="yellow">Cincin ini.
Dimana sekarang?</font>

526
00:57:03,800 --> 00:57:08,000
<font color="yellow">Oh, aku tadi melepasnya saat
aku membantu Bibi Beolgyo.</font>

527
00:57:08,000 --> 00:57:09,590
<font color="yellow">Ta-da!</font>

528
00:57:09,590 --> 00:57:12,800
<font color="yellow">Kau melepasnya?
Cuma sebentar?</font>

529
00:57:12,800 --> 00:57:15,000
<font color="yellow">Hei, kau tahu
jenis cincin apa ini?</font>

530
00:57:15,000 --> 00:57:18,000
<font color="yellow">Aku saja tidak melepasnya selama satu bulan, walau aku mandi sekalipun!</font>

531
00:57:18,000 --> 00:57:20,090
<font color="yellow">Tapi, kau melepasnya
"Cuma sebentar?"</font>

532
00:57:20,090 --> 00:57:22,900
<font color="yellow">Sudahlah!
Aku takkan pernah melepasnya lagi!</font>

533
00:57:22,900 --> 00:57:27,300
<font color="yellow">Sudahlah.
Terserah kau saja.</font>

534
00:57:27,300 --> 00:57:28,690
<font color="yellow">Aku akan melepasnya, menyembunyikannya,
dan membuangnya di suatu tempat!</font>

535
00:57:28,690 --> 00:57:33,900
<font color="yellow">Juga, tidak boleh ada kontak fisik untukmu, selama sebulan!</font>

536
00:57:34,400 --> 00:57:36,000
<font color="yellow">Jangan dekat-dekat aku.</font>

537
00:57:36,000 --> 00:57:39,090
<font color="yellow">Hei, kau marah-marah lagi,
Kang Ji Woon?</font>

538
00:57:39,090 --> 00:57:41,800
<font color="yellow">Wow, kenapa bisa hal sepele
begini selalu membuatmu marah?</font>

539
00:57:41,800 --> 00:57:45,690
<font color="yellow">Aku sudah seperti pacaran
dengan anak kecil saja!</font>

540
00:57:45,690 --> 00:57:49,590
<font color="yellow">Terus, tidak boleh ada kontak fisik?</font>

541
00:57:49,590 --> 00:57:53,300
<font color="yellow">Oh, kita lihat saja siapa yang
bakal lebih menderita.</font>

542
00:57:55,190 --> 00:57:58,000
<font color="yellow">Oh, baiklah.</font>

543
00:57:58,000 --> 00:57:59,690
<font color="yellow">Hei apa yang kaulakukan?
Kau bilang tak boleh ada kontak fisik!</font>

544
00:57:59,690 --> 00:58:01,190
<font color="yellow">Lepas!</font>

545
00:58:01,190 --> 00:58:06,800
<font color="yellow">Hanya saja cincin ini ternyata
sudah lama menghubungkan kita.</font>

546
00:58:06,800 --> 00:58:09,900
<font color="yellow">Aku hanya ingin kau menjaga cincin ini
sebagai benda berharga.</font>

547
00:58:09,900 --> 00:58:12,400
<font color="yellow">Aku juga tahu itu!</font>

548
00:58:12,900 --> 00:58:15,400
<font color="yellow">Mana cincinnya?
Kenapa?</font>

549
00:58:15,400 --> 00:58:16,590
<font color="yellow">Berikan saja padaku.</font>

550
00:58:25,690 --> 00:58:28,800
<font color="yellow">Aku mencintaimu, Eun Ha Won.</font>

551
00:58:31,190 --> 00:58:35,800
<font color="yellow">Yah... Aku juga mencintaimu.</font>

552
00:58:36,900 --> 00:58:39,800
<font color="yellow">Kau masih suka pacaran denganku,
meskipun aku kekanak-kanakan, 'kan?</font>

553
00:58:39,800 --> 00:58:43,800
<font color="yellow">Oh, hentikan, dasar
Tukang Marah! Ugh!</font>

554
00:58:44,690 --> 00:58:48,300
<font color="yellow">Ya ampun, kau keras kepala sekali!
Ayolah!</font>

555
00:58:48,300 --> 00:58:50,090
<font color="yellow">Mau apa kau?/
Jangan marah!</font>

556
00:58:50,090 --> 00:58:51,800
<font color="yellow">Terserah!/ Aku akan menjadi orang yang lebih baik padamu!</font>

557
00:58:51,800 --> 00:58:54,190
<font color="yellow">Katamu tak boleh ada
kontak fisik! Lepas!</font>

558
00:58:54,190 --> 00:58:56,690
<font color="yellow">Ayolah, jangan seperti itu!</font>

559
00:59:18,690 --> 00:59:20,190
<font color="yellow">Kau sudah datang?/
Ya.</font>

560
00:59:28,190 --> 00:59:30,000
<font color="yellow">Kang Seo Woo!</font>

561
00:59:33,090 --> 00:59:34,900
<font color="yellow">BAB-mu pasti langsung keluar,
